The goal is to increase the height of the header section in the leave request PDF generator (`corporatePdf.ts`). This will shift the content sections downwards, reducing the large amount of empty space current present below Section 4 (Contact & Handover) on the first page.

## Proposed Changes

### PDF Library

#### [MODIFY] [corporatePdf.ts](file:///c:/Apps/Leave%20Tracker/src/lib/corporatePdf.ts)

- **Header Spacing**: Increase the spacing before the thick black separator in `drawHeader` and the return value to push content down by ~10-15mm.
- **Inter-section Spacing (Page 1)**: Increase the vertical gaps between Sections 1, 2, 3, and 4.
- **Inter-section Spacing (Page 2)**: Increase the vertical gaps between Sections 5 and 6.

